'''Security Sector Six''' was an area of [[Tipoca City/Legends|Tipoca City]] on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]]. During the [[First Battle of Kamino]], [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]] forces overran the area, [[Death/Legends|killing]] the [[Cloning/Legends|clone]] [[Clone trooper/Legends|Troopers]] guarding it and injuring the [[Unidentified Shistavanen Jedi|Jedi]] commanding them.<ref name="Republic 50">''[[Republic 50]]''</ref>

